snippet.title: The Chandra Law Firm LLC
snippet.description:
The Chandra Law Firm LLC (www.ChandraLaw.com) is a Cleveland, Ohio-based boutique civil-rights and white-collar-criminal-litigation firm with highly credentialed, experienced attorneys who provide passionate, creative, and relentless advocacy for their clients in Ohio and across America.

At Chandra Law, we view ourselves as karmic facilitators™—bending, as Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr. said, the moral arc of the universe toward justice, holding wrongdoers accountable for their bad behavior, and protecting our clients from attack.

We have achieved tremendous results for clients when everything—liberty, property, or reputation—was on the line.

For more information, visit www.ChandraLaw.com.
